    <note>Wen(2) Shiqing [19111] His presumed uncle, Zhengzhong [19110], moved from Zhonghe zhen to Fuchuan zhen in Jian county and Shiqing's family lived in Zhonghe zhen. Shiqing's only surviving son, Anguo [19113], has the same generational name as Zhengzhong's grandson, Anshi [19114], Wen(2) Tianxiang's [19123] great grandfather. It is difficult to believe that these were not members of the same root lineage. Li(2) Hu's [20577] grandson-in-law, Wen(2) Yuanding [20578] was also probably a member of this lineage. Zhou Bida, WJ, 31.14a-15a. CBD, 1, 37.</note>
